20
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:51,380
The Demon Realm is a chaotic place.

21
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,579
Although we have day and night,

22
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,820
rain and snow,

23
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,860
