24
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,100
So we can't see the sun.

25
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:01,540
Yes.

26
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,430
I won't see it anymore.

27
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:11,820
Sister, are you okay?

28
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:16,940
The Formula.

29
00:03:18,820 --> 00:03:20,700
