51
00:04:18,459 --> 00:04:18,899
Sister.

52
00:04:18,899 --> 00:04:20,019
Don't call me sister.

53
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,090
It's none of your business.

54
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,460
But I really can't

55
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:29,780
