56
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,020
like that.

57
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:32,900
My life is up to me.

58
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:37,580
Don't make the same mistake

59
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:39,140
