60
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:39,900
Okay?

61
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,340
My previous life.

62
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:45,780
What happened?

63
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,580
See for yourself,

64
