87
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:41,700
Don’t mess around like before.

88
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:43,700
I don't want to see

89
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:44,980
Mr. Wu or Mr. Wa,

90
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:46,220
