125
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:55,580
My father is doing well.

126
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:56,770
Thank you for your concern.

127
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,900
Will Mr. Wu attend the local imperial exam

128
00:07:59,020 --> 00:08:00,700
