129
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,220
Of course.

130
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,700
I'm not bragging.

131
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:04,900
With the essay I write,

132
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:07,140
