283
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,300
Well...

284
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:15,040
Tell me the truth.

285
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,510
Master.

286
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:17,740
Young Master didn't go out

287
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:19,700
